<div class= "px-4 mt-5 content" id= "overflow-page">
    <h4>OVERFLOW</h4>
    <p class= "mb-1">Use these shorthand utilities for quickly configuring how content overflows an element.</p>
    <hr>
    <p class= "mb-1">Barebones <span class= "text-danger">overflow</span> functionality is provided for two values by default, and they are not responsive.</p>
    <div class= "row mt-3 mb-5">
        <div class= "col-lg-6 agm-bg-light py-3 rounded col-12">
